{
  "name": "message ratings (0122/0127): one standing rating per (rater, message) — flip replaces, tally rides row decorations, leaderboard is RAW NET (a vote is a vote, operator dm#161)",
  "setup": [
    {"op": "register", "id": "alice"},
    {"op": "register", "id": "bob"},
    {"op": "register", "id": "carol"},
    {"op": "channel", "name": "room", "owner": "alice", "members": ["bob", "carol"]},
    {"op": "post", "as": "alice", "channel": "room", "ref": "m1",
     "body": "first result", "status": "fyi"},
    {"op": "post", "as": "alice", "channel": "room", "ref": "m2",
     "body": "second result", "status": "fyi"},
    {"op": "rate", "as": "bob", "channel": "room", "message": "$m1.id", "value": 1},
    {"op": "rate", "as": "bob", "channel": "room", "message": "$m2.id", "value": 1},
    {"op": "rate", "as": "carol", "channel": "room", "message": "$m1.id", "value": -1}
  ],
  "expect": [
    {"call": "messages", "as": "bob", "channel": "room", "since": 0, "match_subset": [
      {"seq": "$m1.seq", "sender": "alice",
       "ratings": {"up": 1, "down": 1, "mine": 1}},
      {"seq": "$m2.seq", "ratings": {"up": 1, "down": 0, "mine": 1}}]},
    {"call": "messages", "as": "carol", "channel": "room", "since": 0, "match_subset": [
      {"seq": "$m1.seq", "ratings": {"up": 1, "down": 1, "mine": -1}}]},

    {"op": "rate", "as": "bob", "channel": "room", "message": "$m1.id", "value": -1},
    {"call": "messages", "as": "bob", "channel": "room", "since": 0, "match_subset": [
      {"seq": "$m1.seq", "ratings": {"up": 0, "down": 2, "mine": -1}}]},

    {"call": "leaderboard", "as": "alice", "channel": "room", "match": {
      "categories": ["general", "trust", "wisdom", "thorough", "helper"],
      "leaderboard": [
        {"target": "alice", "score": -1, "raters": 2,
         "votes": {"up": 1, "down": 2},
         "breakdown": {"general": {"score": -1, "up": 1, "down": 2,
                                   "raters": 2}}}]}},

    {"op": "unrate", "as": "carol", "channel": "room", "message": "$m1.id"},
    {"call": "messages", "as": "carol", "channel": "room", "since": 0, "match_subset": [
      {"seq": "$m1.seq", "ratings": {"up": 0, "down": 1, "mine": 0}}]}
  ],
  "note": "RAW NET (operator final ruling dm#161: 'sum of ALL up and down votes, period'). At the leaderboard step bob holds m1 -1 (flip replaced his +1) and m2 +1, carol holds m1 -1 — so general = 1 up, 2 down, score -1. A vote is a vote: no collapse, score = up - down = sum(categories), one arithmetic at every zoom; `votes` on the global line equals the summed cell counts. Casting mechanics unchanged (one standing rating per rater+message, flip/withdraw); anti-farm is the cast-time daily cap, far above this. DMs included everywhere."
}
